Address:  $HOSTADDRESS$$HOSTLINK$

Service:  $SERVICEDESC$$SERVICELINK$
State:    $PREVIOUSSERVICEHARDSTATE$ -> $SERVICESTATE$ ($NOTIFICATIONTYPE$) since $LASTSERVICESTATECHANGE_REL$
Output:   $SERVICEOUTPUT$
